{
  "texts": [
    "As a result, it is unclear how current literature is connected, what is common and new in each work, and in which direction the field is heading.",
    "This survey seeks to fill this void.",
    "We investigate both supervised and unsupervised papers.",
    "For supervised learning, we identify three shared themes amongst current papers, where samples are matched to either gyroplanes, prototypes, or other samples in hyperbolic space.",
    "For unsupervised papers, we dive into the three main axes explored in current papers, namely generative learning, clustering, and self-supervised learning."
  ]
}